   - This ensures that only one thread can modify these shared resources at a time, preventing race conditions.

2. **Setting `sdev->ud.status` to `SDEV_ST_USED`:**
   ```c
   spin_lock_irq(&sdev->ud.lock);
   sdev->ud.status = SDEV_ST_USED;
   spin_unlock_irq(&sdev->ud.lock);
